file.name: apikey_auth.yaml
file.content:
---
openapi: "3.0.2"
info:
  title: "HTTP Basic Authentication Sample"
  version: "1.0.0"
  description: "Sample Swagger file with HTTP Basic Authentication"
  license:
    name: "Apache 2.0"
    url: "http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html"
servers:
- url: "http://sample.io/api"
paths:
  /operation:
    get:
      responses:
        200:
          description: "All OK"
components:
  securitySchemes:
    api_key:
      type: "apiKey"
      name: "secretKey"
      in: "header"
